{"title":"如何Vibe Coding高颜值UI？","slug":"ykvqo493ab3p2ce6","summary":"在 &quot;Vibe Coding&quot; 的语境下，普通人想要通过 AI 协作搞定高颜值的UI，不需要精通 Figma，只需要掌握以下高杠杆率的指令策略： 1. 放弃“原创”，拥抱“设计系统” 普通人 Vibe coding UI 最大的误区是试图自己发明按钮、自己配色","category":"Vibe Coding技巧","tags":["PART1️⃣ AI设计工作流&Vibe Coding","Vibe Coding技巧"],"featured":false,"order":35,"level":2,"updatedAt":"2026-01-18","wordCount":1151,"sourceUrl":"https://www.yuque.com/abyssalsailor/yg90qa/ykvqo493ab3p2ce6","html":"<p data-lake-id=\"udf0e4c1e\" id=\"udf0e4c1e\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud9a4473d\" id=\"ud9a4473d\">在 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3f1e92b1\" id=\"u3f1e92b1\">&quot;Vibe Coding&quot;</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8c2b426a\" id=\"u8c2b426a\"> 的语境下，普通人想要通过 AI 协作搞定高颜值的UI，不需要精通 Figma，只需要掌握以下高杠杆率的指令策略：</span></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"25fbc487\" id=\"25fbc487\"><span data-lake-id=\"u526309f0\" id=\"u526309f0\">1. 放弃“原创”，拥抱“设计系统”</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u90735cd5\" id=\"u90735cd5\"><span data-lake-id=\"ufefc72f1\" id=\"ufefc72f1\">普通人 Vibe coding UI 最大的误区是试图自己发明按钮、自己配色。</span></p><ul list=\"uce320b69\"><li fid=\"u9cd018fd\" data-lake-id=\"uf0db1be0\" id=\"uf0db1be0\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u8357bff5\" id=\"u8357bff5\">设计原则：</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf034fb23\" id=\"uf034fb23\">一致性 (Consistency)</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4f6b61e6\" id=\"u4f6b61e6\"> 是美感的来源，成熟的系统能保证视觉语言的统一。</span></li><li fid=\"u9cd018fd\" data-lake-id=\"ua3b0faeb\" id=\"ua3b0faeb\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ucb4fc227\" id=\"ucb4fc227\">Vibe Coding 策略：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc0e47afd\" id=\"uc0e47afd\"> 在你的 Prompt 中强制指定成熟的 UI 库。</span></li><li fid=\"u9cd018fd\" data-lake-id=\"u24ab79bc\" id=\"u24ab79bc\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufc0ad701\" id=\"ufc0ad701\">实操指令：</span></strong></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"uc85c819a\" id=\"uc85c819a\"><span data-lake-id=\"u29392325\" id=\"u29392325\">&quot;请使用 </span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6e266656\" id=\"u6e266656\">Shadcn UI</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u33faaa9f\" id=\"u33faaa9f\"> (或 Tailwind CSS) 来构建这个界面。保持风格极简、干净，使用圆角卡片设计。&quot;</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u224ec569\" id=\"u224ec569\"><span data-lake-id=\"u4bf9c562\" id=\"u4bf9c562\">我在之前的一篇笔记里整理了所有审美高级的 UI 组件库，感兴趣的话可以翻翻。</span></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"yuque\" value=\"data:%7B%22mode%22%3A%22card%22%2C%22heightMode%22%3A%22default%22%2C%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fabyssalsailor%2Fyg90qa%2Fvpwsotpi7d04t9ek%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fabyssalsailor%2Fyg90qa%2Fvpwsotpi7d04t9ek%3Fview%3Ddoc_embed%22%2C%22detail%22%3A%7B%22image%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1768724912557-35b0cfc5-2e7c-4888-890b-c8788ca81d71.png%22%2C%22title%22%3A%22VibeCoding%E5%BF%85%E5%A4%87%E5%AE%A1%E7%BE%8E%E9%AB%98%E7%BA%A7%E7%9A%84UI%E7%BB%84%E4%BB%B6%E5%BA%93%22%2C%22type%22%3A%22doc%22%2C%22belong%22%3A%22%E4%BB%BB%E5%A4%A9%E7%9C%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%AE%A4%20%7C%20%E4%BA%A7%E5%93%81%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1%E5%B8%88%E7%9A%84AI%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E5%BA%93%22%2C%22belong_url%22%3A%22%2Fabyssalsailor%2Fyg90qa%22%2C%22desc%22%3A%22%22%2C%22url%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.yuque.com%2Fabyssalsailor%2Fyg90qa%2Fvpwsotpi7d04t9ek%22%2C%22target_type%22%3A%22Doc%22%2C%22extra%22%3A%7B%7D%2C%22_serializer%22%3A%22web.editor_link_detail%22%7D%2C%22id%22%3A%22yM3TJ%22%2C%22margin%22%3A%7B%22top%22%3Atrue%2C%22bottom%22%3Atrue%7D%7D\"></card><p data-lake-id=\"uc5ecfdbf\" id=\"uc5ecfdbf\"><span data-lake-id=\"u44798be9\" id=\"u44798be9\">​</span><br></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"d8a3c1d3\" id=\"d8a3c1d3\"><span data-lake-id=\"u34d06c63\" id=\"u34d06c63\">2. 驯服“留白” (Whitespace is King)</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"ua05e1938\" id=\"ua05e1938\"><span data-lake-id=\"ue5f5cdc8\" id=\"ue5f5cdc8\">新手界面之所以看起来“乱”，通常是因为东西太挤。</span></p><ul list=\"u0a131aeb\"><li fid=\"u55f08210\" data-lake-id=\"ua1e3559f\" id=\"ua1e3559f\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6048c7ad\" id=\"u6048c7ad\">设计原则：</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc7b42178\" id=\"uc7b42178\">呼吸感 (Breathability)</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4ef2b163\" id=\"u4ef2b163\"> 决定了信息的层级和阅读的舒适度，留白本身就是一种设计元素。</span></li><li fid=\"u55f08210\" data-lake-id=\"ub682b4f8\" id=\"ub682b4f8\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u65decd30\" id=\"u65decd30\">Vibe Coding 策略：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u4220bd38\" id=\"u4220bd38\"> 让 AI 增加元素之间的间距。</span></li><li fid=\"u55f08210\" data-lake-id=\"u1dcb8a71\" id=\"u1dcb8a71\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6e3b361d\" id=\"u6e3b361d\">实操指令：</span></strong></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ufd750510\" id=\"ufd750510\"><span data-lake-id=\"ud852203c\" id=\"ud852203c\">&quot;给所有卡片和容器增加更多的内边距（Padding），让内容不要贴边。增加段落和组件之间的垂直间距，让界面看起来更透气、现代。&quot;</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u2f610502\" id=\"u2f610502\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1768710308171-e054d1aa-5613-432d-a6a1-40158b570450.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u793cd504-dc2f-4649-b73f-94cc2835fe9%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u5faf6a93-6ddf-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A756.5%2C%22height%22%3A567%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%221.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A408248%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1079%2C%22originHeight%22%3A809%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22FLEETTRAVELUIKIT%20BIO%20%40VISUAL%20VORTEX%20PURCHASED%20DESIGNWA...%20EDIT%23SSCHEDULE%20CARR%20TH%20AGO%20B%20DIGITEL%20CORE%20DASHBOARD%20BUILDER%201.0%20GEDIT%23SCHEDULE%20%40INNOVATIVE_IDEAS%20PURCHASED%20VIRTUAL...%20128%20TH%20AGO%20LTEMS%20BENTO%20MATTE%203D%20ILLUSTRATION%20%40DESIGN_ENTHUSIAST%20PURCHASED%20FONT....%20EDIT%E7%99%BDSCHEDULE%20TH%20AGO%20COR%20DIGITEL%20BENTO%20DESIGN%20SYSTEM%209%3A41%20JUN%20JUTY%20ALL%20NOTIFICATIONS%20DEC%2015%2C2044%20AT%205%3A30%20PM%20TH%204G9%20OVERVIEW%20LAST%207%20DAYS%209%3A41%209%3A41%209%3A41%20%E4%B8%89%E5%8F%B7%20%E4%B8%BB%E5%8F%B7%20X%20C