0-30-10 原则</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u660dfb7c\" id=\"u660dfb7c\"><span data-lake-id=\"u30c6562e\" id=\"u30c6562e\">普通人容易用太饱和的颜色（纯红、纯蓝），导致界面像 90 年代的网页。</span></p><ul list=\"u34c4e3e9\"><li fid=\"ubb347b14\" data-lake-id=\"u2832f644\" id=\"u2832f644\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2b16bbbf\" id=\"u2b16bbbf\">设计原则：</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uac4de0dd\" id=\"uac4de0dd\">克制 (Restraint)</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue0d7adb3\" id=\"ue0d7adb3\"> 是高级感的关键。主色应占据 60%，辅助色 30%，强调色仅占 10%。</span></li><li fid=\"ubb347b14\" data-lake-id=\"u11c15366\" id=\"u11c15366\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ud68fc131\" id=\"ud68fc131\">Vibe Coding 策略：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3d6dab73\" id=\"u3d6dab73\"> 限制 AI 的调色盘，多用无彩色（黑白灰）。</span></li><li fid=\"ubb347b14\" data-lake-id=\"u0bd2c097\" id=\"u0bd2c097\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ue8c75a40\" id=\"ue8c75a40\">实操指令：</span></strong></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u3d4ef74d\" id=\"u3d4ef74d\"><span data-lake-id=\"u02b9d436\" id=\"u02b9d436\">&quot;主色调使用深灰色或黑色，背景使用米白色或浅灰色（Off-white）。只在按钮或关键行动点（CTA）上使用唯一的亮色（比如品牌蓝）。不要使用高饱和度的纯色。&quot;</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"uaed3167e\" id=\"uaed3167e\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1768710261245-68a4000c-307f-40a1-9380-22a37d02ef99.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u8958fd93-b095-467c-b761-4e3a161bae8%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u5faf6a93-6ddf-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A1024%2C%22height%22%3A768%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A655136%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A2048%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1536%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22DAILY%20MONTHLY%20WEEKLY%209%3A41%209%3A41%20STRETCHING%20AFTER%20WORKOUTS%20IMPROVES%20YOUR%20SLEEP%20QUALITY.%20HOW%20MAN%20LET'S%20START%20BURN%20YEST%20DISMISS%20SET%20ROUTINE%20STRONG!%20YOU%20BURNED%20