-lake-id=\"u335ecc1f\" id=\"u335ecc1f\"> 引导视线。通过字重、字号和颜色的深浅来区分信息的重要性。</span></li><li fid=\"u41131a9f\" data-lake-id=\"udd2b8508\" id=\"udd2b8508\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua0d0161e\" id=\"ua0d0161e\">Vibe Coding 策略：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u54a59479\" id=\"u54a59479\"> 明确告诉 AI 哪些是重点，哪些是次要。</span></li><li fid=\"u41131a9f\" data-lake-id=\"u0e685f20\" id=\"u0e685f20\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua86b19d2\" id=\"ua86b19d2\">实操指令：</span></strong></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"u3132cacc\" id=\"u3132cacc\"><span data-lake-id=\"u3d200db2\" id=\"u3d200db2\">&quot;优化排版层级：让主标题（H1）非常醒目；次要信息使用灰色（text-gray-500）和较小的字号；确保正文有良好的行高（leading-relaxed）以利于阅读。&quot;</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u63806181\" id=\"u63806181\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1768720380443-5175e734-8db1-4890-93fa-999237ea9c0d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22ucfaaf71e-e78f-462b-81f0-5fe2ee34abc%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u5faf6a93-6ddf-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A1024%2C%22height%22%3A768%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A1087694%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A2048%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1536%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22X%20FINYON%20TECHNOLOGY%20VIEW%20DEMO%20ABOUT%20PRICING%209%3A41%20PAYMENT%20SYSTEM%20FINANCE%20MADE%20SIMPLE%20FOR%20ENTREPRENEURS%20WHETHER%20YOU'RE%20LAUNCHING%2CGROWING%2COR%20SIMPLY%20SEEKING%20A%20SMARTER%20WAY%20TO%20HANDLE%20YOUR%20MONEY%2C%20HOPE%20CREDIT%20UNION%20IS%20HERE%20TO%20HELP.%20B%2011%206.2K%20567%20SUCCESSFUL%20FUNDING%20ROUNDS%20BUSINESSES%20SUPPORTED%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A193%2C%22y%22%3A199%2C%22width%22%3A159%2C%22height%22%3A43%2C%22text%22%3A%22X%20FINYON%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A1409%2C%22y%22%3A206%2C%22width%22%3A94%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22TECHNOLOGY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A176