3A1282%2C%22width%22%3A177%2C%22height%22%3A19%2C%22text%22%3A%22BUSINESSES%20SUPPORTED%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23c0ba5b%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u5fedff99%22%7D\"></card></p><h3 data-lake-id=\"06789240\" id=\"06789240\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1ab4669b\" id=\"u1ab4669b\">5. 注入“微质感” (The 1% Detail)</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u49b1b85b\" id=\"u49b1b85b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u1f84e199\" id=\"u1f84e199\">最后这一步是区分“像个 Demo”和“像个产品”的关键。</span></p><ul list=\"ud96203c4\"><li fid=\"u5d757869\" data-lake-id=\"ubc0989f4\" id=\"ubc0989f4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uf85e949c\" id=\"uf85e949c\">设计原则：</span></strong><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u00a1d147\" id=\"u00a1d147\">物理隐喻 (Physical Metaphor)</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u2dde5191\" id=\"u2dde5191\"> 增加真实感。阴影和边框暗示了层级关系。</span></li><li fid=\"u5d757869\" data-lake-id=\"u592e7223\" id=\"u592e7223\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ueebbc9f5\" id=\"ueebbc9f5\">Vibe Coding 策略：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u7668935b\" id=\"u7668935b\"> 添加微妙的装饰性属性。</span></li><li fid=\"u5d757869\" data-lake-id=\"u20ad13c2\" id=\"u20ad13c2\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"ufa288392\" id=\"ufa288392\">实操指令：</span></strong></li></ul><p data-lake-id=\"ub8d1e9f0\" id=\"ub8d1e9f0\"><span data-lake-id=\"uc16dcb74\" id=\"uc16dcb74\">&quot;给所有卡片添加一个极细微的边框（border-gray-200）和柔和的阴影（shadow-sm）。给按钮添加 hover 状态的反馈动画。&quot;</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"u0980c2f2\" id=\"u0980c2f2\"><card type=\"inline\" name=\"image\" value=\"data:%7B%22src%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.nlark.com%2Fyuque%2F0%2F2026%2Fpng%2F1206632%2F1768720599532-d15606e7-f9a0-4684-b378-ab23b0519e1d.png%22%2C%22taskId%22%3A%22u9ac6a8da-cf75-432b-8378-141b7bc2ffc%22%2C%22clientId%22%3A%22u5faf6a93-6ddf-4%22%2C%22originalType%22%3A%22binary%22%2C%22width%22%3A459%2C%22height%22%3A459%2C%22linkTarget%22%3A%22_blank%22%2C%22name%22%3A%22image.png%22%2C%22size%22%3A497685%2C%22from%22%3A%22paste%22%2C%22originWidth%22%3A1200%2C%22originHeight%22%3A1200%2C%22ratio%22%3A2%2C%22status%22%3A%22done%22%2C%22style%22%3A%22none%22%2C%22search%22%3A%22GENERATING%20TERMS%20PRIVACY%20COOKIE%20POLICY%20POLICY%20OF%20USE%20AL%20COMPLIANCE%20COPILOT%20ENSURE%20FULL%20GLOBAL%20COMPLIANCE%20WITH%20JUST%20A%20SINGLE%20CLICK%22%2C%22ocrLocations%22%3A%5B%7B%22x%22%3A536%2C%22y%22%3A355%2C%22width%22%3A167%2C%22height%22%3A31%2C%22text%22%3A%22GENERATING%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A733%2C%22y%22%3A571%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22TERMS%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A336%2C%22y%22%3A571%2C%22width%22%3A94%2C%22height%22%3A29%2C%22text%22%3A%22PRIVACY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A536%2C%22y%22%3A573%2C%22width%22%3A89%2C%22height%22%3A24%2C%22text%22%3A%22COOKIE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A335%2C%22y%22%3A604%2C%22width%22%3A80%2C%22height%22%3A28%2C%22text%22%3A%22POLICY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A536%2C%22y%22%3A604%2C%22width%22%3A79%2C%22height%22%3A25%2C%22text%22%3A%22POLICY%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A735%2C%22y%22%3A606%2C%22width%22%3A78%2C%22height%22%3A22%2C%22text%22%3A%22OF%20USE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A290%2C%22y%22%3A744%2C%22width%22%3A469%2C%22height%22%3A48%2C%22text%22%3A%22AL%20COMPLIANCE%20COPILOT%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A290%2C%22y%22%3A817%2C%22width%22%3A562%2C%22height%22%3A44%2C%22text%22%3A%22ENSURE%20FULL%20GLOBAL%20COMPLIANCE%22%7D%2C%7B%22x%22%3A288%2C%22y%22%3A881%2C%22width%22%3A419%2C%22height%22%3A32%2C%22text%22%3A%22WITH%20JUST%20A%20SINGLE%20CLICK%22%7D%5D%2C%22showTitle%22%3Afalse%2C%22title%22%3A%22%22%2C%22rotation%22%3A0%2C%22crop%22%3A%5B0%2C0%2C1%2C1%5D%2C%22averageHue%22%3A%22%23fcfdfa%22%2C%22id%22%3A%22u6ca9abe2%22%7D\"></card></p><card type=\"block\" name=\"hr\" value=\"data:%7B%22id%22%3A%22gNF96%22%7D\"></card><h3 data-lake-id=\"e69909f7\" id=\"e69909f7\"><span data-lake-id=\"u95aadce0\" id=\"u95aadce0\">用一段话优化你的 vibe coding 产品</span></h3><p data-lake-id=\"u022c8c41\" id=\"u022c8c41\"><span data-lake-id=\"u2f520028\" id=\"u2f520028\">你可以直接复制这段话发给 AI 进行一键美化：</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ub54e8f9b\" id=\"ub54e8f9b\"><span data-lake-id=\"u7fae78c4\" id=\"u7fae78c4\">&quot;请优化当前 UI 的视觉设计，使其看起来像一个现代的 SaaS 产品。</span></p><ol list=\"u4e79f8e9\"><li fid=\"ufbab44cb\" data-lake-id=\"u831fafd1\" id=\"u831fafd1\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u56a8c44b\" id=\"u56a8c44b\">风格：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"ua1bdaf6f\" id=\"ua1bdaf6f\"> 使用 Shadcn UI 风格，极简、干净、圆角。</span></li><li fid=\"ufbab44cb\" data-lake-id=\"ufc7ae5a4\" id=\"ufc7ae5a4\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"uc5656059\" id=\"uc5656059\">布局：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u9bd45405\" id=\"u9bd45405\"> 增加所有容器的内边距和组件间距，保持呼吸感。</span></li><li fid=\"ufbab44cb\" data-lake-id=\"ufc432976\" id=\"ufc432976\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u051566db\" id=\"u051566db\">色彩：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u22ea1a69\" id=\"u22ea1a69\"> 使用黑白灰为主色调，仅在 CTA 按钮使用[你喜欢的颜色]。</span></li><li fid=\"ufbab44cb\" data-lake-id=\"u8bd38211\" id=\"u8bd38211\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u0c9ca62b\" id=\"u0c9ca62b\">排版：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u6513d428\" id=\"u6513d428\"> 增强文字层级对比，次要文字用灰色。</span></li><li fid=\"ufbab44cb\" data-lake-id=\"uc09eb2ca\" id=\"uc09eb2ca\"><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u33d2d4db\" id=\"u33d2d4db\">细节：</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u656b17ab\" id=\"u656b17ab\"> 给卡片添加微妙的边框和阴影。&quot;、</span></li></ol><p data-lake-id=\"u65d80972\" id=\"u65d80972\"><span data-lake-id=\"ucf653bb3\" id=\"ucf653bb3\">​</span><br></p><p data-lake-id=\"u134f9de6\" id=\"u134f9de6\"><span data-lake-id=\"u925d6196\" id=\"u925d6196\">在 Vibe Coding 时代，技术门槛消融，审美成为了区分“Demo”与“产品”的关键分水岭。高级感并非依靠艺术天赋，而是源于对克制、留白与秩序的理性坚守。</span><strong><span data-lake-id=\"u03a66e3f\" id=\"u03a66e3f\">普通人无需成为专业设计师，只需掌握核心原则，用 Prompt 驾驭 AI。</span></strong><span data-lake-id=\"u3384275f\" id=\"u3384275f\">用逻辑构建美，也让理性的代码拥有打动人心的力量。</span></p><p data-lake-id=\"ue8d524e5\" id=\"ue8d524e5\"><br></p>"}
